<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">6月28日，省教育厅社办党委调研组第二小组一行三人至我校调研基层党建“三化”建设工作。学校在行政楼204会议室召开汇报会。党委书记、督导专员江延湖出席会议，党委委员、组织部部长程杨胜，党委委员、统战部部长康婧，学院党总支书记代表参加会议。</span></p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A26%3A0222880c72d5fb04201dfa66db6ab471b.jpg?Expires=2035077963&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=xkjXoZEelmln3atkENIOL4%2FdGGE%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A26%3A0222880c72d5fb04201dfa66db6ab471b.jpg?Expires=2035077963&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=xkjXoZEelmln3atkENIOL4%2FdGGE%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></span></p><p style="text-align:center;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">在会议上，江延湖对调研组的到来表示热烈欢迎及衷心的感谢，并简要汇报了学校近些年发展、学校基层党建“三化”建设等情况。检查组通过现场查看、个别访谈、及时反馈等方式，对学校基层党建“三化”建设情况进行了全面的检查，并提出改进意见。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A26%3A35d4cd800b5b942d0a88b2fd6f957f3f2.jpg?Expires=2035077996&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=MVtNjLWWvI55rBNKrF7UZYRoUns%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A26%3A35d4cd800b5b942d0a88b2fd6f957f3f2.jpg?Expires=2035077996&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=MVtNjLWWvI55rBNKrF7UZYRoUns%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/>&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">汇报会后，调研组来到网络工程学院，通过听取网络工程学院党总支书记、专职组织员汇报、查阅了“三会一课”记录本等材料。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">对于本次调研，调研组充分肯定了我校党建工作取得的成绩，针对实地检查过程中发现的问题，调研组现场提出了相应的意见及建议。学校党委将认真落实好调研组的指示要求，丰富基层党建“三化”建设载体，突出特色，努力打造党建品牌，以高质量党建促进学校事业高质量发展。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">调研期间，调研组还走访了学生食堂、宿舍，对学校安全管理进行了同步检查。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A28%3A34db22f16d6e4cefdb75de8b761126e13.jpg?Expires=2035078115&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ffZmgTODpul7dBnLeTkrhqPB270%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(35, 82, 124); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-06-30%2011%3A28%3A34db22f16d6e4cefdb75de8b761126e13.jpg?Expires=2035078115&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ffZmgTODpul7dBnLeTkrhqPB270%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></span></p><p><br/></p>